This is how to build GhostRacer in a macOS Terminal window, assuming you've
already installed XQuartz and freeGLUT:

1. Download project with:
        git clone https://github.com/NingWang1729/GhostRacer.git
2. To build the program, change into the GhostRacer directory and type:
        make
3. To run the program, type:
        ./GhostRacer
